Action: calc
Action Input: {"expression": "120*2 + 4*2 + 15*2"}

Thought: Hostel prices in Yangshuo start as low as €3.70 (~$4) per night [serp_2], and bike rentals cost around ¥15 ($2) per day [serp_4]. I now have enough data to estimate total costs for a 2-day trip. I will calculate transportation (round-trip train + local bus), accommodation (1 night), food, and activities.

